comments.value: -- stagger the heartbeats of selected elements to so that they indicate the order of selection
-- check if the drawn text is the selected function, and if so group a beating rectangle behind it

{- , "  |> "
                   ++ stampString m m.draw
                   ++ (if m.draw == Outlined then
                           styleString m ++ " "
                       else
                           ""
                      )
                   ++ clrString m m.clr
                   |> code
                   |> move ( 0, -10 )
                -}

{- }
                   , ( "solider"
                     , TransM
                           (\m ->
                               { m
                                   | alpha =
                                       if m.alpha < 1 then
                                           m.alpha + 0.125
                                       else
                                           1
                               }
                           )
                     )
                   , ( "ghostier"
                     , TransM
                           (\m ->
                               { m
                                   | alpha =
                                       if m.alpha > 0 then
                                           m.alpha - 0.125
                                       else
                                           0
                               }
                           )
                     )
                   , ( "bigger"
                     , TransM
                           (\m ->
                               { m
                                   | scl =
                                       if m.scl < 3 then
                                           m.scl + 0.25
                                       else
                                           3
                                   , sclx =
                                       if m.sclx < 3 then
                                           m.sclx + 0.25
                                       else
                                           3
                                   , scly =
                                       if m.scly < 3 then
                                           m.scly + 0.25
                                       else
                                           3
                               }
                           )
                     )
                   , ( "smaller"
                     , TransM
                           (\m ->
                               { m
                                   | scl =
                                       if m.scl > -3 then
                                           m.scl - 0.25
                                       else
                                           -3
                                   , sclx =
                                       if m.sclx > -3 then
                                           m.sclx - 0.25
                                       else
                                           -3
                                   , scly =
                                       if m.scly > -3 then
                                           m.scly - 0.25
                                       else
                                           -3
                               }
                           )
                     )
                -}

{- ( "clockwise", TransM (\m -> { m | angle = m.angle - 30 }) )
                     , ( "counter", TransM (\m -> { m | angle = m.angle + 30 }) )
                     ,
                  -}
